      <section>
         <ol>
            <li>All sites must develop a formal Traffic Management Plan with suitable pedestrian/vehicle segregation.</li>
            <li>The plan shall include rules for safe designating parking, refueling/charging,
               repairing, and moving of disable vehicles.</li>
            <li>The plan shall include the provision of signs, speed limits, barriers, bollards, walk ways, etc.</li>
         </ol>
      </section>
